<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.5">
<l>arakka rāvi māḷa vaṉṟu  vāḻka ṭalcū ḻilaṅkai ceṟṟa</l>
<l>kurakka raca ṉeṉṟuñ kōla villi yeṉṟum māma tiyai</l>
<l>rukku māṭa nīṭu nāṅkai niṉma laṉtā ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟōti</l>
<l>parakka ḻintā ḷeṉma ṭantai pārttaṉ paḷḷi pāṭu vāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “King of monkeys who destroyed Lanka encircled by the deep sea</l>
<l>That day when the demon’s breath expired,” saying, “He of the shapely bow,”</l>
<l>Reciting over and over, “He is the immaculate one of spacious Nāṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">where mansions press the huge moon,”</l>
<l>She fell into disgrace; my simple girl sings of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
